description:
In episode 773, Jack and Miles are joined by Scam Goddess and comedian Laci Mosley to discuss young MAGA, Trump flipping on Georgia, the Fox Town Hall, five day old gas station sushi hallucinations, the Neilsen ratings, and more!

FOOTNOTES:

  1. Young Republicans Stage Secret Gala, Ignoring Virus Concerns

  4. Woman hallucinates for months after eating five-day-old gas station sushi
  5. ‘The Queen’s Gambit’ Rules U.S. Streaming Chart, With Disney’s ‘The Mandalorian’ Breaking Through To The No. 3 Spot
